snippet.title: Free Realms Trailer
snippet.description: Free Realms is the first free-to-play MMORPG developed by the legendary MMO studio, Sony Online Entertainment. The game is set in a humorous fantasy world, and removes typical MMO boundaries such as class and level, instead encouraging player freedom and social gameplay. Players can switch between a variety of jobs from adventurer to kart driver, raise a pet, and more, all on the same character.
